Package: speedConversion
Type: Package
Title: Functions for speed units conversion.
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-07-26
Author: Purnima Dasgupta <purnima.dasgupta27@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Purnima Dasgupta <purnima.dasgupta27@gmail.com>
Description: The package contains a list of functions that convert units of
    speed (specially windspeeds) from one unit to another. There are 10 sets of
    unit conversions therefore 20 functions inlcuding vice-versa cases. All
    conversion formulae are sourced from National Weather Service and Weather
    Forecast Office (NOAA).
License: MIT
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
